	(text "OPTO-ISOLATED RELAY DRIVER\nESP32 GPIO (3.3V) to R5 (330 Ohm) to PC817 LED to GND\nPC817 phototransistor to R6 (1K) to Q1 Base\nQ1 Collector to Relay Coil (SRD-05VDC) to VCC_5V\nD4 flyback protection across coil\nD5 TVS across relay contacts for arc suppression"
